\n<Burilla>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Why you hurt Zuki?!\.\. The Sufferer just cured Zuki head!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<Burilla>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Leave Zuki alone!\.\. Got mission!\.\. Zuki no go back there!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]

\n<Burilla>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Zuki paid for her cures with a promise,\. Zuki had to search you...\.\.\. but Zuki got lost...\.\.\. surface people didn't let Zuki search for the Sufferer's cub...\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<Burilla>\fs[\v[320]]\fn<\v[319]>Sufferer in Deep Deep now...\.\.\. Zuki now go tell her he found the cub!!\fn<GameFont>\fs[30]
\n<Wandering Monk>Every night,\. I come here at the Monument to pray for the ones that lost their lives in the Hole.
\n<Wandering Monk>May their souls find their way out untainted.
\n<Soldier>We'll get the prize!\.\. We'll be RICH!!
\n<Soldier>Thank you fer dealin' with the huge fella over there,\. cat.\.\. I'm sure there's a lesson fer ya somewhere in this...
\n<Soldier>Th' garrison cap'n want us to deal with THAT huge thing?!
\n<Soldier>Aye,\. am not waking it up,\. got two kids t' feed...
\n<Soldier>Oh,\. I know a good one,\. furry!\.\. If ye can do some'ing,\. don't do it fo' free!
\n<Soldier>Aye we got th' request from the \c[18]Committee\c[0] back in town...\.\.\. but am not feelin' it right now...
\n<Soldier>Ye want to take care it off our hands,\. kitten?\.\. 'Ts got a nice reward...\.\.\.
\n<\n[1]>Rewards?\.\. \G?!\.\. I'll do it,\. scaredy cats!\.\. Actually,\. only I can do it around here~
\n<Soldier>Try not t' get killed,\. will ya?\.\.
\n<Soldier>We got no coin t' spare for the dead,\. after all~
\n<\n[1]>Am not getting close to the fat blob over there,\. forget about it.
\n<Soldier>Aye aye...\.\.\. looks too tough for ya,\. doesn't it?
